Package net.dean.jraw.models.attr

Contains attributes (interfaces) that can be applied to models

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Created
    Indicates that this model was created
    Distinguishable
    Indicates this Thing was posted by a redditor of elevated role in the website, such as an administrator or moderator.
    Gildable
    Specifies that this model is able to be given Reddit Gold
    Votable
    Provides a way to show that this Thing is able to be voted on
